title: ToysRUs: Diggin Skootcase Only $24.98 (Regularly $59.99) – Makes Traveling w/ Kids Fun
text:
Traveling with little ones soon? Hop on over to ToysRUs.com where they have this Diggin Skootcase priced at just $24.98 (regularly $59.99)! This seems like a great deal since Amazon currently has this same item priced at $48.99!

This Italian inspired scooter has a hollow interior that can be used to store clothing, supplies, and other items on your trip. It rolls easily on rubber wheels and provides entertainment for the kiddos at the airport. It also features a shoulder strap for easy carrying, and fits in the overhead bin on airplanes.

Shipping is free on orders over $29 OR opt for free in-store pickup if available at a store near you.
